  
  Now it is time to learn how to run nuclei templates... 
    
    1. Step 1: Decide on a template that you want implement
       URL 1: https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates
       URL 2: https://nuclei.projectdiscovery.io/nuclei/get-started/
       URL 3: https://nuclei.projectdiscovery.io/nuclei/get-started/#nuclei-config
       
    2. Step 2: Find a proper image having this vulnerability, and make this image run on your local or wherever you want...
    
       App will be seen at http://related-ip:related-port
    
    3. Step 3: Start an attack from nuclei to the target url that the vulnerable app is running on...
    
       nuclei -u https://related-ip:related-port -t cves/2021/CVE-2021-44228.yaml 
    
      


    
